<section class="hero">
  <h1>Manual-check leads</h1>
  <p class="lede">Sources the scraper does <strong>not</strong> auto-collect — either community forums (leads, not structured listings) or agency/lead-gen portals (low owner-direct yield). Worth a manual scan, especially the ones marked candidates for a future adapter.</p>
